<!--
    TheWatch Launcher Icon Foreground - Shield Vector Drawable
    ===========================================================
    A shield icon representing safety and security, centered within
    the 108dp adaptive icon canvas. The visible area is the inner 72dp
    (18dp padding on each side for parallax/masking).

    Design notes:
      - Shield shape symbolizes protection and emergency response
      - Inner cross/plus symbolizes first-responder / medical assistance
      - Designed at 108x108dp canvas per adaptive icon spec
      - Viewable safe zone: 72x72dp centered

    NOTE: For production release, replace this vector with the final
    brand-approved icon from your design team. This placeholder is
    functional and renders correctly across all adaptive icon shapes.

    Reference: https://developer.android.com/develop/ui/views/launch/icon_design_adaptive
    Canvas: 108dp x 108dp, safe zone: 72dp x 72dp (centered)
-->
